track_notes: You must be healthy to reach the summit using this way, the landscape is very fine! in winter you must have snowshoes or sky. In summer just a hat and some water.
Need good shoes and good health

This is a very long walk to reach this summit, therefor it is best in summer than in winter when sunrise is ealy. The starting point is on a forest road which is very small and best if you have a 4x4.
Plenty room on summit for antenna.
